There‚Äôs a few ways that can be done. One is to just use Coast mode, but that‚Äôs not going to provide much resistance. Another is to temporarily turn the P value low, making it a much weaker ‚Äúspring‚Äù. I‚Äôm not sure exactly how they do it, or what degree of compliance vs resistance is required for their purpose.
